&lt;h1&gt;Administration Assistant, Cardiology - Band 2 &lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a part time admin assistant to join the administrational team within Cardiology; we offer a supportive environment within an enthusiastic and motivated team with no two days the same. The post holder will require excellent administrational skills and interpersonal skills to support a multidisciplinary team and Cardiology patients. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will need good keyboard and computer skills and will cover clerical and administrative tasks. Full training will be given. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details please contact Mandy Beech Admin Manager for the Cardiology Department 01225 826130 or email mandybeech@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
